Part 2

Time felt as if it had stopped and the world was frozen. His heart beat was rapid and cold sweat trickled down his forehead. She had a face he could never truly forget even if he tried.

From her expression, it seems that even she was shocked to see him. Nervously, he opened his mouth to speak.

"I-Inoue-san...?"

Fin
(thanks to the Nanashi1831daremo for the inspiration)

Working at the company, Maeda was constantly restless during meetings as he was unable to focus. He had a sort of trauma and almost everyone in the company knew about it. However, nobody knew what sort of trauma it was.

His superior told him to get a break from work and meet a psychiatrist to help with his trauma. He obliged with the request of his superior and searched out for a doctor to help him. At the hospital, he was diagnosed to a particular doctor that was the best at handling mental traumas sex related.

After waiting for his turn, he entered the doctor's room. After entering, he sat down on the chair waiting for the doctor to arrive. He heard the door opening and looked behind him.

The doctor had a familiar face and the atmosphere around her was something he was all too familiar with. Her face was not something he could forget even if he tried to.
